item.title: CVE-2023-32468|2024-10-21T13:07:54.722Z -- dell -- ecs%20streamer
item.description: Dell ECS Streamer, versions prior to 2.0.7.1, contain an insertion of sensitive information in log files vulnerability. A remote malicious high-privileged user could potentially exploit this vulnerability leading to exposure of this sensitive data.
